{"calories":"790","carbs":103,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eIf any ingredient can make a humble plate of pasta feel like a million dollar meal, it’s truffle zest, a seasoning made from always swanky truffles. Here, Chef Michelle adds the seasoning to buttery toasted breadcrumbs for a luxurious garnish. For the pasta, she sautés mushrooms with shallots and thyme before folding into a velvety white wine–cream sauce. With one bite of this decadent dish, dinner becomes a black tie affair.\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"a7a0ca14d5","fat":28,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/hero_voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/menu_small_voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/small_square_voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/medium_square_voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41871/recipe_profile_page_voqkK0dvReqJcfruU1Sd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41873/ygTlJaaJSbGJIYcqZc98_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0208___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41873/menu_small_ygTlJaaJSbGJIYcqZc98_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0208___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41874/large_cropped_77R7JwY7SFWhuzzuefrd_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0210___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41872/H19JUha4SDaBzznYv2by_Creamy_Mushroom_Pasta_with_Truffle_Butter_Breadcrumbs_and_Chives___0212___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}}],"name":"Creamy Mushroom Linguine with Truffle Breadcrumbs and Chives","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":26,"public_slug":"creamy-mushroom-pasta-with-truffle-butter-breadcrumbs-and-chives","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/25266/recipe_card20180223-10-6728i9.pdf","recipe_id":4197,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Creamy Mushroom Linguine","subtitle":"with Truffle Breadcrumbs and Chives","title":"Creamy Mushroom Linguine","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003ePanko breadcrumbs can burn quickly, so keep an eye on them and stir constantly as they toast.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse the leftover cream to enrich mashed potatoes, scrambled eggs, or a pureéd vegetable soup. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eKeep adding the starchy pasta cooking water until the sauce is silky and clings to the linguine—you may need more than you think.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot ","10\" medium high-sided pan"],"id":4197,"ingredients":["chives","shallot","unsalted butter","panko breadcrumbs","truffle zest","thyme","linguine","white wine","heavy cream","grated Parmesan cheese","cremini mushrooms","oyster mushrooms"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"chives","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1281/medium_square_medium_square_chives-2-test.jpg"},{"name":"shallot","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/130/medium_square_SHALLOT_copy.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"panko breadcrumbs","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/21/medium_square_PANKO_BREADCRUMBS_copy.jpg"},{"name":"truffle zest","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1661/medium_square_truffle_zest.jpg"},{"name":"thyme","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1289/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"linguine","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/65/medium_square_linguini-1.jpg"},{"name":"white wine","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/256/medium_square_WHITE_WINE_copy.jpg"},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2301/medium_square_HEAVY_CREAM_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2309/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"cremini mushrooms","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/326/medium_square_cremini-mushrooms-test2.jpg"},{"name":"oyster mushrooms","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":100,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/609/medium_square_oyster-mushrooms.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41875/recipe_card_size_DwNBd3HBTTmuyJz4mzZN_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eBring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Wipe \u003cstrong\u003emushroom\u003c/strong\u003e caps clean with a damp paper towel (so they don't absorb water and brown better in the pan) and cut into .25-inch slices. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003echives \u003c/strong\u003eand thinly slice. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eshallots\u003c/strong\u003e and mince. \u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toast breadcrumbs","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41876/recipe_card_size_YADAIAsYRgCqNSMGJBVC_2._Toast_Breadcrumbs.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e1 packet butter\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003ebreadcrumbs\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring, until golden and toasted, 2-3 minutes (see recipe tip). Remove pan from heat, and stir in \u003cstrong\u003etruffle zest\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003e.125 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eto combine. Transfer to a small bowl and set aside, reserving pan for next step.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Sauté mushrooms","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41879/recipe_card_size_833bkQFRQe3unBkAYvI6_3._Cook_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e2 teaspoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in pan from breadcrumbs over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003ethyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eshallots\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring, until softened, 2-3 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003emushrooms\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring occasionally, until golden and crisp, 8-10 minutes (move on to Step 4, but don't forget to come back!). Remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ethyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e. Season mushrooms with \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41878/recipe_card_size_eZ2aLzzQQ0qoAabHTsHG_4._Cook_Pasta.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mushrooms cook, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003elinguine\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 8 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain and set aside.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish mushroom pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41877/recipe_card_size_a4F4OJsRRnSfc0imrSqA_5._Finish_Mushroom_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce mushrooms are cooked, add \u003cstrong\u003ewine\u003c/strong\u003e to pan, still over medium-high heat, and stir until almost evaporated, about 1 minute. Add \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup cream\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until warmed through, 1-2 minutes more (see recipe tip). Remove pan from heat, and stir in \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003elinguine\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eremaining butter\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of reserved pasta water \u003c/strong\u003eto combine. Stir in remaining pasta cooking water, 1 tablespoon at a time, until sauce is thickened (see recipe tip).\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate mushroom pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/41880/recipe_card_size_JIpsdsh3RrO8nlQ7VtsE_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eTaste \u003cstrong\u003epasta\u003c/strong\u003e and add \u003cstrong\u003esalt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Divide \u003cstrong\u003ecreamy mushroom linguine\u003c/strong\u003e between serving plates and top with \u003cstrong\u003etruffle breadcrumbs\u003c/strong\u003e. Garnish with \u003cstrong\u003echives \u003c/strong\u003eand dig in!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[{"name":"Soy","slug":"soy","hex_color":""},{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Stovetop only","slug":"stovetop-only","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}